{"id": "5613", "post": "<div class=\"post-5613 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-budapest tag-hungary tag-microvps-eu tag-openvz tag-xen tag-xenpv\" id=\"post-5613\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/mikrovps-3-85month-256mb-xen-5-64quarter-256mb-ovz-and-more-in-hungary/\" rel=\"bookmark\">MikroVPS \u2013 $3.85/month 256MB Xen, $5.64/quarter 256MB OVZ and more in Hungary</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/budapest/\" rel=\"tag\">Budapest</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/hungary/\" rel=\"tag\">Hungary</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/microvps-eu/\" rel=\"tag\">microvps.eu</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\" rel=\"tag\">openvz</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xenpv/\" rel=\"tag\">xenpv</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> August 12, 2014 @ 1:00 am, by Maarten Kossen</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://www.mikrovps.eu\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTg4IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE4OCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/MikroVPS_Cost-effective_IT_solutions_-_2014-08-11_15.24.22-300x188.png.webp\" alt=\"MikroVPS_Cost-effective_IT_solutions_-_2014-08-11_15.24.22\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\"></a>Janos, from <a href=\"https://www.mikrovps.eu\" target=\"_blank\">MikroVPS</a>, is back with several offers in Budapest, Hungary! These offers include both Xen and OpenVZ machines of various sizes. I\u2019ve listed four of the plans I was sent, but you are free to use the coupon code <strong><strong>LEB2014</strong></strong> for their other plans to get 40% off the regular price! MikroVPS are a company who were founded in April 2012 as a sole trader by <a href=\"http://www.domain.hu/domain/English/domainsearch/whois.html?domain=mikrovps.hu&amp;ekes=mikrovps.hu\">Janos</a> himself. This is the second time we\u2019re featuring them here. Since last time, they have also started offering OpenVZ offers. They use SuperMicro-based servers with AMD CPUs, which is rather uncommon. Personally I like to see offers with AMD CPUs, as it broadens the landscape we have here. Host nodes have either a AMD Opteron 4280 (OpenVZ) or 4386 (Xen) CPU, 32GB of RAM, 4x 1TB hard drives in RAID10 backup up by a RAID controller with BBU. Each VPS is assigned 1 IPv6 address but more are available for free upon request. All prices exclude VAT which only needs to be paid if you are from the EU and do not have a valid VAT number. I\u2019m looking forward to hear any experiences you guys have with MikroVPS, so feel free to share them in the comments.</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong><strong>XEN-256M</strong></strong><p></p><ul><li>256MB RAM</li><li>256MB Swap</li><li>2 vCPUs (weight: 10)</li><li>10GB HDD space</li><li>500GB traffic</li><li>1Gbit uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>1x IPv6</li><li>XenPV/SolusVM</li><li>Promo code:&nbsp;<strong><strong>LEB2014</strong></strong></li><li>\u20ac2.95/month</li><li>$3.85/month</li><li><a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/cart.php?a=add&amp;language=English&amp;currency=2&amp;pid=171&amp;promocode=LEB2014\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong><strong>XEN-512M</strong></strong><p></p><ul><li>512MB RAM</li><li>512MB Swap</li><li>2 vCPUs (weight: 20)</li><li>30GB HDD space</li><li>1500GB traffic</li><li>1Gbit uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>1x IPv6</li><li>XenPV/SolusVM</li><li>Promo code: <strong><strong>LEB2014</strong></strong></li><li>\u20ac4.33/month</li><li>$5.64/month</li><li><a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/cart.php?a=add&amp;language=English&amp;currency=2&amp;pid=171&amp;promocode=LEB2014\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong><strong>VZ-256</strong></strong><p></p><ul><li>256MB RAM</li><li>1 vCPU</li><li>10GB HDD space</li><li>100GB traffic</li><li>1Gbit uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>1x IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Promo code: <strong><strong>LEB2014</strong></strong></li><li>\u20ac4.33/quarter</li><li>$5.64/quarter</li><li><a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=174&amp;language=English&amp;currency=2&amp;promocode=LEB2014\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong><strong>VZ-512</strong></strong><p></p><ul><li>512MB RAM</li><li>2 vCPUs</li><li>25GB HDD space</li><li>250GB traffic</li><li>1Gbit uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>1x IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Promo code: <strong><strong>LEB2014</strong></strong></li><li>\u20ac5.12/quarter</li><li>$6.66/quarter</li><li><a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=175&amp;language=English&amp;currency=2&amp;promocode=LEB2014\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span id=\"more-5613\"></span></p><p>Payments are made via PayPal at the moment, with a non-refund policy. They provide a 99.86% uptime guarantee per calendar month according to their <a href=\"http://www.mikrovps.eu/gtc\">Terms of Service</a>. They allow IRC for personal usage as well as VPN and proxies, Tor is permitted \u201cwithin the framework of legality\u201d although I wouldn\u2019t be sure how they would monitor that, as well as legal adult content being permitted. Downloading films or music for personal usage is permitted too. According to Janos, they have a traffic limit in place but only suspend the VPS in the event illegal activity is noticed.</p><p><strong>Network Information</strong></p><p>Servers are located in Budapest, Hungary at the <a href=\"http://doclerweb.com/\">DoclerWeb </a>facility.</p><p>Test IPv4: 188.227.227.71<br>\nTest IPv6: 2001:950:1:23::3<br>\nTest files: <a href=\"http://test.mikrovps.hu/50mb.test\" target=\"_blank\">50MB</a> | <a href=\"http://test.mikrovps.hu/100mb.test\" target=\"_blank\">100MB</a> | <a href=\"http://test.mikrovps.hu/1G.test\" target=\"_blank\">1GB </a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fmikrovps-3-85month-256mb-xen-5-64quarter-256mb-ovz-and-more-in-hungary%2F&amp;t=MikroVPS%20-%20%243.85%2Fmonth%20256MB%20Xen%2C%20%245.64%2Fquarter%20256MB%20OVZ%20and%20more%20in%20Hungary\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=MikroVPS%20-%20%243.85%2Fmonth%20256MB%20Xen%2C%20%245.64%2Fquarter%20256MB%20OVZ%20and%20more%20in%20Hungary&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fmikrovps-3-85month-256mb-xen-5-64quarter-256mb-ovz-and-more-in-hungary%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fmikrovps-3-85month-256mb-xen